2026-02-25T23:26:38Z | 7c6298af4bc6dcb520735c67cdc9315bcf9a591b | Fix admin gate login loop

Refactor useAdminGate to handle new successful payload, add guards to prevent duplicate login calls, and ensure single initialization:
- Accept data.data.session_token from admin-gate and store in sessionStorage
- Use hasInitializedRef and isLoginInProgressRef to prevent repeated login attempts
- Add isAuthenticated and loading guards in useEffect to avoid loop
- Update login flow to process data.success or data.code === 'SUCCESS' and extract token accordingly
- Maintain existing logout behavior

Result: admin login no longer loops, token saved correctly, and initialization happens once.

